00:16:31,919 --> 00:16:32,919
As people always say,

276
00:16:33,359 --> 00:16:34,400
in this world, to women,

277
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:35,799
father, brother

278
00:16:36,159 --> 00:16:37,039
husband and son

279
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:39,000
are whom they depend on,

