00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:42,080
but in the end, they should depend on

281
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:44,039
themselves.

282
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:50,520
(Admonitions for Women)

283
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,520
When I was your age,

284
00:16:53,599 --> 00:16:54,679
I also read "Admonitions for Women".

285
00:16:57,159 --> 00:16:58,400
What do you think?

286
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:02,640
I've long forgotten

287
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,880
about the lessons taught in the book.

288
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,559
However, that sentence,

289
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,280
"teach men but not women,

290
00:17:07,479 --> 00:17:09,359
isn't that also bigotry?"

291
00:17:09,719 --> 00:17:10,520
left a lasting impression to me.

292
00:17:11,959 --> 00:17:13,359
Ban Zhao edited "Book of Han",

293
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:15,880
which means he wasn't
a short-sighted person.

294
00:17:16,959 --> 00:17:19,000
Although "Admonitions for Women"
were lessons for women,

295
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,680
it's possible to glimpse the first light

296
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:23,400
between the lines.

297
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:25,560
It's the hopes of Ban Zhao

298
00:17:25,959 --> 00:17:27,000
which was for men and women

299
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:29,280
to learn courtesy and knowledge.

300
00:17:30,119 --> 00:17:31,079
That's why you

301
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:33,160
decided to teach women knowledge.

302
00:17:34,079 --> 00:17:34,760
Xiaoman,

303
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:36,760
remember this.

304
00:17:37,319 --> 00:17:38,239
Even after you get married,

305
00:17:38,520 --> 00:17:40,640
you must also remain strong
despite the circumstances,

306
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,199
and never let your
initial ambition falter.

307
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:44,920
Although you'll be in
Commandery Prince's Mansion,

308
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,839
you can also learn knowledge

309
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:47,920
and be a prolific reader.

310
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:49,199
That way,

311
00:17:49,479 --> 00:17:50,479
you won't get caught

312
00:17:50,479 --> 00:17:51,959
in the typical complaints by females

313
00:17:52,319 --> 00:17:54,439
or the troubles of daily life.

314
00:17:56,079 --> 00:17:57,040
Only with ambition will a woman

315
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:59,239
not be affected by external factors.

316
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:02,800
Thank you, Teacher Liu.

317
00:18:03,599 --> 00:18:05,479
I'll definitely keep your
teachings in mind

318
00:18:06,280 --> 00:18:07,239
so I could be like you

319
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:09,119
without losing my initial ambition.

320
00:18:21,199 --> 00:18:22,520
Stand forth, the protagonist of
the coming-of-age ceremony.

321
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:12,880
The first cap is bestowed
upon you on this joyous day.

322
00:19:13,479 --> 00:19:16,359
You're to rid yourself of childishness
and acquire virtues of adulthood.

323
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:20,839
By doing so, you will live a long and
happy life and have good fortune.

324
00:19:27,359 --> 00:19:29,239
She will stand at the chamber
on the left side.

325
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:32,079
Stand forth, the protagonist of
the coming-of-age ceremony.

326
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:42,160
Tasty sweet wine and
dried meat are presented

327
00:19:42,599 --> 00:19:45,239
to the ancestors for
blessing to the nation.

328
00:19:45,800 --> 00:19:48,800
Thanks to heaven's blessing, a good
reputation will always be remembered.

329
00:19:56,359 --> 00:19:58,880
Since the ceremony is ready,
on this joyous day,

330
00:19:59,599 --> 00:20:02,359
you'll be given a formal name.
It's a great name,

331
00:20:03,079 --> 00:20:05,800
which goes well with the scholar.
A suitable name is the topmost priority.

332
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:09,400
So, keep it well for the rest of your
lifetime. You shall be called Fu An.

333
00:20:10,239 --> 00:20:11,239
Although I'm not smart,

334
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,280
I couldn't offer my respect enough.

335
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:26,680
Serve the tea.

336
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:07,959
Filial to the parents, take care
of the juniors with kindness.

337
00:21:09,040 --> 00:21:12,400
Temperate, kind, courteous,
restrained and magnanimous.

338
00:21:13,560 --> 00:21:17,400
Don't get conceited or arrogant.
Don't slander or deceive.

339
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:22,239
Traditional lessons are a
formality which you must keep.

340
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:53,640
(I hope everything will go well
for Xiaoman from now on.)

341
00:21:54,599 --> 00:21:55,479
(For the family of three)

342
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:57,719
(to be happy always.)

343
00:24:12,180 --> 00:24:15,780
(Lotus Garden)

344
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:22,920
What's wrong?

345
00:24:23,479 --> 00:24:24,040
Are you afraid?

346
00:24:25,359 --> 00:24:26,199
Who says I'm afraid?

347
00:24:27,199 --> 00:24:28,319
Playing chess is my hobby, that's all.

348
00:24:30,239 --> 00:24:31,280
If it's in the past,

349
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:32,719
I'll let you take two steps first.

350
00:24:33,439 --> 00:24:35,079
Too bad today's your wedding day.

351
00:24:35,599 --> 00:24:36,680
The circumstances don't favour me.

352
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:45,479
I won by half a chess piece.

353
00:24:47,119 --> 00:24:47,800
Go ahead.

354
00:24:49,839 --> 00:24:50,599
Let's play another game.

355
00:24:50,599 --> 00:24:51,199
Let's play another game.

356
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:52,599
Come on. Come on.

357
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:56,359
Hurry.

358
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,360
Stop.

359
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:19,959
Let them go.

360
00:25:24,660 --> 00:25:26,660
(Lotus Garden)

361
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:43,880
Move aside.

362
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,280
Mistress asked me to toss coins
and dried fruits at the bed.

363
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,400
Do you know the rules or not?

364
00:25:56,599 --> 00:25:57,520
Don't touch those.

365
00:25:57,959 --> 00:25:59,160
If you're hungry,

366
00:25:59,319 --> 00:26:00,599
I'll cook you a bowl of noodles.

367
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:02,520
No need.

368
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:03,640
I'm not hungry.

369
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:05,680
Let me tell you.

370
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:07,880
It's not that my lady
doesn't want me anymore.

371
00:26:08,119 --> 00:26:10,000
I'm going back to the Residence
of the Su Family soon.

372
00:26:10,239 --> 00:26:10,800
Wick,

373
00:26:12,599 --> 00:26:13,280
tell me.

374
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:15,880
Will he

375
00:26:16,719 --> 00:26:17,319
want to

376
00:26:18,479 --> 00:26:19,400
consummate with me?

377
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:20,920
What's wrong with that?

378
00:26:21,239 --> 00:26:22,160
For a married couple,

379
00:26:22,359 --> 00:26:23,599
it's just normal.

380
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,839
Haven't you heard of those words before?

381
00:26:27,520 --> 00:26:28,479
Toss coins and dried fruits at the east,

382
00:26:28,719 --> 00:26:30,239
a lovely pair of lotuses
embroidered on the bed.

383
00:26:30,599 --> 00:26:31,479
Toss coins and dried fruits at the west,

384
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:32,959
a pair of golden roosters
embroidered on the bed.

385
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,280
Toss coins and dried fruits
at the north,

386
00:26:34,439 --> 00:26:35,520
the couple will have children easily.

387
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:36,400
Toss coins and dried fruits
at the south,

388
00:26:36,599 --> 00:26:37,599
there'll be an abundance of offspring.

389
00:26:38,199 --> 00:26:39,199
I'll even have to give birth to a child?

390
00:26:39,199 --> 00:26:39,959
Of course.

391
00:26:40,199 --> 00:26:41,680
If the newlyweds sleep
on the same side,

392
00:26:41,800 --> 00:26:43,160
they'll have a pair
of children next year.

393
00:26:43,520 --> 00:26:44,959
The son will be the principal graduate
in the palace examination

394
00:26:45,079 --> 00:26:46,400
and the daughter will be
a princess consort.

395
00:26:47,520 --> 00:26:48,560
What princess consort?

396
00:26:51,560 --> 00:26:52,920
The daughter will be a princess consort.

397
00:26:53,119 --> 00:26:54,800
Which is to say, if Your Highness

398
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:56,199
has a daughter with Lady Xiaoman,

399
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:58,280
she'll become a princess consort
in the capital.

400
00:26:58,280 --> 00:26:59,040
Wick.

401
00:27:00,359 --> 00:27:01,119
Well said.

402
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,319
Go and get a reward from Liangji.

403
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:04,239
Thank you, Your Highness.

404
00:27:21,439 --> 00:27:23,719
Did you get into a fight again?

405
00:27:25,479 --> 00:27:27,040
I thought you won't
talk with me anymore.

406
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:30,280
I've promised you.

407
00:27:30,760 --> 00:27:31,839
If I keep on giving you an attitude,

408
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:33,400
I'd also feel bad.

409
00:27:35,760 --> 00:27:36,520
Are you hungry?

410
00:27:37,239 --> 00:27:38,280
I saw you busying
yourself the entire day

411
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:39,719
and didn't seem to eat anything.

412
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:42,520
I prepared some venison jerky for you.

413
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:44,520
If you're hungry...

414
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:45,280
Don't come over.

415
00:27:54,119 --> 00:27:54,959
I have to sit down

416
00:27:55,520 --> 00:27:56,439
or it's against the manners.

417
00:28:06,860 --> 00:28:10,420
(Commandery Prince's Mansion)

418
00:28:15,599 --> 00:28:16,560
Where's Commandery Prince of Julu?

419
00:28:17,599 --> 00:28:18,400
His Highness...

420
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:24,000
Zhu Momo.

421
00:28:25,079 --> 00:28:26,000
Where's Commandery Prince of Julu?

422
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:27,400
His Highness is inside.

423
00:28:31,439 --> 00:28:32,400
She's sent here from the capital.

424
00:28:33,460 --> 00:28:35,860
(Lotus Garden)

425
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:40,400
Don't come over.

426
00:28:41,719 --> 00:28:42,400
Go ahead and shout.

427
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,920
Why aren't you shouting anymore?

428
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:48,479
Shouted yourself hoarse, haven't you?

429
00:28:50,199 --> 00:28:50,760
Come over.

430
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:52,839
You...

431
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:54,000
Come and drink
this wedding toast with me.

432
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:04,319
People do that when
they marry their wives.

433
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,439
I'm just a concubine.

434
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,400
Draping red ornaments
all over your room,

435
00:29:09,719 --> 00:29:11,199
people might say I have no manners.

436
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:12,880
Why do you bother?

437
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,640
I was worried you'll be wronged.

438
00:29:18,079 --> 00:29:18,680
Take it.

439
00:29:18,680 --> 00:29:19,400
That's the rule.

440
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:44,760
Come over.

441
00:29:51,319 --> 00:29:52,439
If one of the cups faces upward
and the other downward,

442
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:54,199
it's an auspicious sign
with symbolic meaning.

443
00:29:54,520 --> 00:29:55,599
The crowd will then offer
their congratulatory wishes.

444
00:29:57,839 --> 00:29:58,920
That's a good sign.

445
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:00,439
In the future, we'll

446
00:30:01,359 --> 00:30:02,239
lead a good life.

447
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:08,839
Don't go overboard!

448
00:30:10,560 --> 00:30:11,719
This time, it's our master.

449
00:30:20,199 --> 00:30:21,040
Zhu Momo's here.

450
00:30:21,239 --> 00:30:22,000
What she's doing here?

451
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:22,839
Hurry up! Hurry!

452
00:30:23,479 --> 00:30:24,319
Who is she?

453
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:25,400
The housekeeper.

454
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:27,359
Hurry!

455
00:30:30,560 --> 00:30:31,959
Greetings, Momo.

456
00:30:33,319 --> 00:30:34,400
All these ornaments in the house

457
00:30:35,199 --> 00:30:36,239
are too improper.

458
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:39,400
Commandery Prince of Julu
doesn't know the customs.

459
00:30:39,719 --> 00:30:40,319
Liangji,

460
00:30:40,959 --> 00:30:42,839
you're from Prince of Pu's Mansion.

461
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:44,079
Don't you know the customs?

462
00:30:45,040 --> 00:30:46,079
Pardon me.

463
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,439
Inform Commandery Prince of Julu that

464
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:48,560
I'm here.

465
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:50,599
Zhu Momo's here.

466
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:54,719
Greetings, Zhu Momo.

467
00:31:02,839 --> 00:31:03,680
Zhu Momo?

468
00:31:04,719 --> 00:31:05,400
What's wrong?

469
00:31:08,079 --> 00:31:09,000
Someone came from the capital.

470
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,359
She's my mother's nanny.

471
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:12,560
Don't speak later.

472
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:20,500
(Lotus Garden)

473
00:31:28,040 --> 00:31:30,119
I've disturbed Your Highness's rest.

474
00:31:30,760 --> 00:31:32,040
Please forgive me.

475
00:31:32,719 --> 00:31:33,599
Zhu Momo,

476
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:35,800
why are you here?

477
00:31:36,560 --> 00:31:37,599
Your Highness's willful actions

478
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:39,640
caused some trouble in the capital.

479
00:31:39,959 --> 00:31:43,079
Her Highness wanted me to bring
this message to Your Highness.

480
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:06,680
Since you're getting a concubine,

481
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:07,760
why?

482
00:32:08,079 --> 00:32:09,800
The bride's in a red costume.

483
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,719
Is she going to be the duchess?

484
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,920
I told them to make the wedding dress.

485
00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:15,560
It has nothing to do with Xiaoman.

486
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:18,119
Come at me if there's anything.

487
00:32:18,719 --> 00:32:20,439
His Highness doesn't
know the customs.

488
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:21,640
Liangji,

489
00:32:22,079 --> 00:32:23,599
are you also not aware of it?

490
00:32:24,239 --> 00:32:25,400
His Highness is a royal.

491
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:28,000
Therefore, he should follow the rules.

492
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:30,680
Today, the concubine's
wearing a red costume.

493
00:32:31,199 --> 00:32:33,079
In the future, when the duchess
marries into the family,

494
00:32:33,199 --> 00:32:34,239
what's she going to wear?

495
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:41,160
Zhu Momo,

496
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:42,560
we weren't considerate enough.

497
00:32:43,239 --> 00:32:45,079
Lady Xie was our classmate.

498
00:32:45,359 --> 00:32:46,160
Hanchen's getting a concubine

499
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:47,520
and everyone's happy.

500
00:32:48,239 --> 00:32:50,079
In fact, this isn't exactly red either.

501
00:32:50,479 --> 00:32:51,439
We told them

502
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,719
not to make it bright red.

503
00:32:53,119 --> 00:32:54,000
We added mauve colour

504
00:32:54,959 --> 00:32:55,880
to differentiate

505
00:32:56,199 --> 00:32:58,000
as well as to add to the festivities.

506
00:32:58,959 --> 00:33:00,680
That's right. Mauve colour was added.

507
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:02,920
All right, that's that.

508
00:33:03,959 --> 00:33:05,439
Since she's married into the family,

509
00:33:06,239 --> 00:33:08,760
I won't pursue what
happened in the past.

510
00:33:09,479 --> 00:33:11,479
However,
I was sent here by Her Highness.

511
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:14,160
So, I should follow
Prince of Pu's Mansion's rules.

512
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:17,760
Since Lady Xie is the concubine,

513
00:33:18,439 --> 00:33:19,319
within the mansion,

514
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:21,400
she's just a maidservant.

515
00:33:22,719 --> 00:33:25,680
Prince of Pu's Mansion never allowed
a person with no manner to stay.

516
00:33:34,040 --> 00:33:34,880
Lady Xie,

517
00:33:35,119 --> 00:33:36,479
show me your courtesy.

518
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:43,079
Zhu Momo, you came all
the way from the capital.

519
00:33:43,079 --> 00:33:44,000
It must be a tiring journey.

520
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:46,280
Why don't you take a rest first?

521
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:47,040
Carry it properly.

522
00:33:49,479 --> 00:33:50,119
Zhu Momo!

523
00:33:50,599 --> 00:33:51,719
This is Commandery Prince's Mansion,

524
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:52,920
not Prince of Pu's Mansion!

525
00:33:54,520 --> 00:33:56,040
Since you're now a prince,

526
00:33:56,680 --> 00:33:58,520
you should be cautious with
your words and actions more.

527
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:00,319
Let's not talk about
Prince of Pu's Mansion.

528
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:03,280
Even at Zichen Palace in the capital,

529
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:06,520
which of the ladies has no manners?

530
00:34:07,479 --> 00:34:08,680
Since you're from Zhao Family

531
00:34:09,439 --> 00:34:11,560
and respected by the people,

532
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:14,719
you should follow the people's rules.

533
00:34:18,120 --> 00:34:18,719
Tomorrow,

534
00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:21,399
Lady Xie will rise at 5.45 a.m. to

535
00:34:21,879 --> 00:34:24,280
learn manners from me first.

536
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:27,040
But I have to go to
the academy tomorrow.

537
00:34:43,919 --> 00:34:44,760
Lady Xie,

538
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:48,199
you're so naive.

539
00:34:49,159 --> 00:34:50,479
No married woman

540
00:34:50,679 --> 00:34:52,919
can leave her mansion freely.

541
00:34:53,439 --> 00:34:54,159
Moreover,

542
00:34:54,479 --> 00:34:56,760
now that you're married,

543
00:34:57,159 --> 00:34:58,800
you don't have to go to
the academy anymore.

544
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:02,800
What's the purpose of
going to the academy anyway?

